<div style="width:0;height:0;clear:both"></div><dl class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-">
<dd class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-title">
<h1>CISSP</h1>
<a class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" href="javascript:;" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=1436764" nslog-type="90000102" target="_blank"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num">999</span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">CISSP 英文全称：“ Certified Information Systems Security Professional”，中文全称：“(ISC)²注册信息系统安全专家”，由(ISC)²<sup class="normal"></sup>组织和管理，是目前全球范围内最权威，最专业，最系统的<a data-lemmaid="5979238" href="/item/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81/5979238" target="_blank">信息安全认证</a>。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
(ISC)²注册信息系统安全专家
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">外文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
Certified Information Systems Security Professional
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">简    称</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
CISSP
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">性    质</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
最权威，最专业的<a href="/item/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81" target="_blank">信息安全认证</a>
</dd>
</dl></div>
